-- =====================================================
-- Arizona (AZ) Medical Malpractice Rules
-- Enhanced Verification Protocol v2.0
-- =====================================================
-- State: Arizona
-- Governing Law: ARS § 12-561 et seq. (Medical Malpractice Actions)
-- Negligence Model: PURE COMPARATIVE FAULT (ARS § 12-2505)
-- SOL: 2 years from discovery (ARS § 12-542)
-- Damage Caps: NONE — Arizona Constitution Art. 18 § 6 prohibits caps on damages
-- Certificate of Merit: Preliminary expert affidavit REQUIRED at filing (ARS § 12-2603)
-- =====================================================

-- RULE 1: STANDARD OF CARE
